PROFESSOR: Let's get started.

00:00:25.090 --> 00:00:26.540
Drop date is coming up.

00:00:26.540 --> 00:00:28.499
So that you didn't do
very well on the midterm,

00:00:28.499 --> 00:00:30.206
and you haven't been
doing your homework,

00:00:30.206 --> 00:00:32.070
