00:11:45.340 --> 00:11:49.290
As you can see, the years
have not been kind to Carol.

00:11:49.290 --> 00:11:52.720
And your tuition only
does goes so far.

00:11:52.720 --> 00:11:55.840
Now, we need three volunteers.

00:11:55.840 --> 00:11:57.760
We're going to play
the game three times.

00:11:57.760 --> 00:11:59.600
All right, got a couple there.

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:00.690
Why don't you come down?

00:12:00.690 --> 00:12:03.180
We've got three volunteers here.

00:12:03.180 --> 00:12:08.490
All right, we'll get
the boxes set up.

00:12:08.490 --> 00:12:10.090
And Carol, why don't
you set those up

00:12:10.090 --> 00:12:14.660
and load them up with-- these
are the gift certificates.

00:12:14.660 --> 00:12:16.645
That's the pocket
protector there.

00:12:16.645 --> 00:12:17.770
All right, now, don't look.

