00:18:44.500 --> 00:18:48.490
to use intuition or
hand waving arguments.

00:18:48.490 --> 00:18:51.610
Now, for example,
this game-- Carol

00:18:51.610 --> 00:18:54.220
wants to leave-- yeah, Carol,
let's give Carol a hand here.

